text: i liked this spot. had a hige pitcher of margarita here and staggered around the square. i wonder if anything's going to open in it's place ever?
Yeah. It's supposed to be reopening somewhere else sometime, I think. But it's closed now. And it wasn't that great. Oh well.

So gross. Not accommodating at all. I ordered a burrito with no cheese or meat, just fajita veggies. Easy enough, right? No. They brought me a flour tortilla filled with RAW VEGETABLES. When I tried to explain that I wanted them cooked, they were indignant. This place is lame. Go to El Cid.
